beer.beer_description: We set out to create a mainstay IPA that was approachable but packed full of flavour. Harnessing Simcoe, Ekuanot, Citra, Centennial hops; we think we have found that optimal balance. With its hazy golden allure - the aromas and flavours lean towards your orange, pine and caramel malt notes.
